              "id": "Ji0kI",
              "fill": "$--muted-foreground",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "A will only protects your family if it is written and signed correctly for the laws that apply to your assets. We guide you through Kenya’s requirements in plain English so you understand every decision.",
